msgstr "这是一个全息投影仪，激活时会生成一个交互式全息影像。全息影像可以与你交谈，回答你的一些问题，但最重要的是，它能定位工厂。"

#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Projector - Locator of Military Outpost"
msgid_plural "Hologram Projector - Locator of Military Outposts"
msgstr[0] "全息投影仪 - 军事前哨定位器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Projector - Locator of Military
#. Outpost'}
#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This is a hologram projector which generates an interactive hologram when "
"you activate it. Hologram can talk to you, answer some of your questions, "
